eply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Fear again for 2 bard whips and some other epic stuff</span><hr size=1> Let's compare.<br>
<br>
Compete against many players in Hate/Fear for armor drops, and THEN go to Kael and work your butt off for significantly better gear.<br>
<br>
-or-<br>
<br>
Go work your butt off in Kael and skip the time consuming process of Hate/Fear.<br>
<br>
You don't have to go to the arena right off the bat.  Hit the manor for awhile and get your core plate classes geared.  By the time you're done there, you WILL be able to do the arena with 1, maybe 2, groups. <p><br><center><a href="http://www.unhomed.com">
