Go to the big raids when they are planned (if people are leading them where you want to go, try start out simple and get some raid leading experience and then take the masses where you want to go).  Try to get a few people together for pickup groups to different places between the big planes raid.<br>
More of an &quot;and&quot; situation than an &quot;either/or&quot; <p><br><br>
